20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fmethodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20homeowners%20insurance%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22865%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20writer%20Veneta%20Lusk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68094521c6ad288d147ef63e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22433%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Veneta%20Lusk.%3Cp%3EVeneta%20Lusk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20have%20homeowners%20insurance%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20too%20worried%20when%20my%20floor%20started%20leaking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20many%20types%20of%20water%20damage%20aren't%20covered%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20can%20be%20costly%20to%20file%20a%20claim.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20paying%20out%20of%20pocket%2C%20but%20I'm%20also%20adding%20a%20rider%20to%20my%20insurance%20to%20protect%20me%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20water%20coming%20up%20between%20two%20of%20the%20wood%20floor%20planks%20in%20my%20kitchen%2C%20I%20suspected%20there%20was%20a%20water%20leak.%20Something%20similar%20had%20happened%20when%20I%20was%20renting%20a%20townhouse%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20it%20had%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20dishwasher%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fbest-homeowners-insurance-companies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeowners%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20figured%20I%20was%20covered%20for%20any%20water%20damage%20to%20my%20kitchen%2C%20including%20the%20floor%20and%20cabinets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20water%20was%20in%20front%20of%20the%20refrigerator%2C%20so%20I%20checked%20both%20the%20refrigerator%20and%20the%20dishwasher%2C%20but%20they%20were%20both%20dry.%20A%20thorough%20look%20under%20the%20kitchen%20sink%20cabinet%20also%20showed%20no%20signs%20of%20water%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20quick%20call%20with%20my%20plumber%2C%20I%20continued%20monitoring%20the%20spot%20where%20I%20first%20saw%20water.%20He%20suggested%20calling%20a%20leak%20detection%20service%20if%20I%20saw%20any%20more%20water%20coming%20up%20between%20the%20floorboards.%20While%20I%20saw%20no%20more%20water%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20the%20wood%20started%20warping%20and%20getting%20wavy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226df5e123-7584-4a72-bbbc-426c4311585c%5C%22%3EMore%20water%20and%20floor%20damage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20before%20I%20planned%20to%20go%20on%20a%20trip%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20wood%20floors%20in%20front%20of%20my%20sink%20bubbled%20up%20and%20started%20creating%20a%20hump.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20I%20heard%20water%20squishing%20under%20the%20hump%20when%20I%20stepped%20on%20it.%20The%20leak%20had%20gotten%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20weren't%20any%20signs%20of%20a%20leak%20from%20the%20fridge%2C%20dishwasher%2C%20or%20sink.%20It%20was%20time%20to%20schedule%20the%20leak%20detection%20company%20to%20come%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20was%20about%20to%20leave%20town%20shortly%2C%20I%20scheduled%20the%20leak%20detection%20company%20to%20come%20out%20when%20I%20got%20home.%20While%20I%20was%20gone%2C%20I%20had%20the%20city%20turn%20off%20the%20water%20to%20my%20house%20to%20ensure%20I%20didn't%20return%20to%20a%20flooded%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leak%20detection%20company%20ran%20several%20tests%20to%20determine%20if%20I%20had%20a%20slab%20leak%20or%20something%20else.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20copper%20kitchen%20water%20drain%20pipe.%20The%20leak%20detection%20cost%20me%20%24395.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20house%20was%20built%20in%201968%20and%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20pipes%20running%20throughout%20%E2%80%94%20PEX%20pipes%2C%20PVC%20pipes%2C%20and%20copper%20pipes%20among%20them.%20My%20plumber%20said%20that%20copper%20pipes%20are%20bound%20to%20fail%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd38d81c-847b-4473-b7d0-99071cac4df8%5C%22%3EWater%20damage%20often%20isn't%20covered%20by%20homeowners%20insurance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Wes%20Slater%2C%20a%20private%20client%20advisor%20with%20HUB%20Private%20Client%2C%20a%20division%20of%20full-service%20global%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fwhat-is-insurance-broker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurance%20brokerage%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hubinternational.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHUB%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20water%20claims%20make%20up%20about%20a%20third%20of%20all%20insurance%20claims%20in%20the%20U.S.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20water%20damage%20is%20covered.%20Slater%20says%20sudden%20and%20accidental%20leaks%2C%20such%20as%20a%20pipe%20breaking%2C%20are%20usually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fwhat-does-homeowners-insurance-cover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecovered%20by%20homeowners%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20policies%2C%20but%20slow%20leaks%20over%20time%20may%20not%20be.%20Most%20homeowners%20insurance%20policies%20cover%20flooding%20from%20sewer%20or%20drain%20backups%20only%20if%20the%20policy%20includes%20a%20special%20rider.%20In%20addition%2C%20water%20from%20a%20storm%20is%20generally%20covered%20under%20separate%20flood%20insurance%20or%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fhomeowners-insurance-endorsements-riders-floaters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeowners%20insurance%20riders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20estimates%20for%20fixing%20the%20drain%20pipe%20ranged%20between%20%24440%20and%20%241%2C200.%20I%20ended%20up%20paying%20%24440%20and%20am%20happy%20with%20the%20fix%20and%20having%20the%20water%20back%20on.%20The%20plumber%20had%20to%20cut%20into%20two%20of%20my%20cabinets%20to%20fix%20the%20pipes.%20My%20next%20step%20was%20to%20find%20a%20contractor%20to%20fix%20the%20cabinets%20and%20replace%20the%20damaged%20floors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239786f2c-5e50-4c72-b929-8f362ff8d776%5C%22%3EFixing%20the%20damage%20is%20costly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20getting%20the%20leak%20detected%20and%20fixing%20the%20pipes%20cost%20me%20%24835%2C%20the%20biggest%20cost%20is%20fixing%20the%20damage%20caused%20by%20the%20water%20leak.%20I%20have%20wood%20floors%20throughout%20my%20entire%20house%2C%20and%20my%20kitchen%20is%20open%20to%20the%20dining%20room%20and%20living%20room.%20This%20means%20I%20needed%20to%20consider%20how%20much%20of%20the%20kitchen%20floor%20I%20could%20replace%20without%20having%20to%20replace%20the%20floors%20in%20the%20entire%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20I%20have%20some%20extra%20boxes%20of%20floorboards%20that%20could%20help%20patch%20up%20the%20areas%20damaged%20by%20water.%20However%2C%20it%20would%20require%20moving%20a%20few%20things%20around%20to%20see%20how%20far%20the%20water%20damage%20extends.%20Right%20now%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20this%20will%20cost%20me%20around%20%241%2C500%20to%20%242%2C000%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20much%20higher%20depending%20on%20the%20required%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227df90d96-6579-4283-aece-ff495f01e749%5C%22%3EIt%20might%20not%20be%20worth%20filing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20repairing%20my%20floors%20could%20set%20